snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade - Season V: Legacy of Fire Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
You can’t start a fire without a spark. Rage through the flames of history in Season V: Legacy of Fire, coming to Conqueror's Blade as a free update on October 13! Learn more: https://conqblade.com/news/585
